<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich Ochsen, Schultheiß von Bamberg</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Befragung des zu Bamberg gefangen genommenen Diebs und bittet um Bericht wegen des in Nürnberg gefangen genommenen Mittäters.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_8" id="2v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_8_r2l22">F Ochſen <expan>Schulth<ex>eiſʒ</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l23">cʒu Bamberg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_8_r2l24"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Schultheiſʒ / vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> die nach dem dyeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l25">vnd <expan>ſchedlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> manne 
<del rend="strikethrough">n <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan></del> nehſt beẏ ew cʒu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l26">ſein / wol geſagt / vvie daʒ Jr Jn ın <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ire<ex>n</ex></expan> ſachen gar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l27"><expan>fürderlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd gewegen ſeit geweſen / des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erb<ex>erkeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l28"><expan>fleiſʒıkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>dancke<ex>n</ex></expan> / Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſıe vns geſagt / vvie daʒ ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_line_1570449671546_205">derſelb dyeb in geheim wol geſagt hab / vvaʒ Er 
<del rend="strikethrough">alles </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_8_line_1570449596114_181">alles </ab></add> getan vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l32">begangen hab / darümb <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_8_r2l30">an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> <expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ew das </ab><ab facs="#facs_8_line_1570613924683_488"><expan>fugl<ex>lich</ex></expan> ſey </ab></add> <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l33">wöllet laſſen wiſſen / waʒ ew derſelb dẏeb alſo in geheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l34">geſagt hab 
<add><ab facs="#facs_8_r1l1"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> waʒ Jr von </ab><ab facs="#facs_8_r1l2">Jm <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt </ab></add> / Eʒ ſeẏ von des gelts / das Er hıe <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_8_r2l37"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_8_r2l35">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ew das fu </del></ab></add> / daʒ wır vns mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> der ſein geſelle iſt </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_9" id="3r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_9_r1l2">
<add>geweſen</add> vnd hie bey vns <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> ligt auch darnach <expan>gerıht<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_9_r1l3">mügen / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir das wol in geheim halten wollen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_9_r1l4">das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_8" id="2v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>F<ex>ridrich</ex></expan> Ochsen, <expan>schulth<ex>eisz</ex></expan>
                        czu Bamberg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her schultheisz, uns
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die
                        nach dem dyeb und <expan>schedlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> manne nehst bey ew czu
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, wol gesagt, wie daz ir in in
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ire<ex>n</ex></expan> sachen gar <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und gewegen seit gewesen, des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>erkeit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleiszikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>dancke<ex>n</ex></expan>. Auch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sie uns
                        gesagt, wie daz ew derselb dyeb in geheim wol gesagt hab, waz er
                            <add>alles</add> getan und begangen hab. Darümb
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir uns <add>an
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>, <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ew das
                                    <expan>fugl<ex>lich</ex></expan> sey</add>,
                                <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet lassen wissen, waz ew
                        derselb dyeb also in geheim gesagt hab <add><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> waz
                            ir von im <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt</add>, ez sey
                        von des gelts, das er hie <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat,
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> sache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir
                        uns mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>, der sein geselle ist <pb facs="#facs_9" id="3r"/><add>gewesen</add> und hie bey uns <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ligt, auch darnach <expan>geriht<ex>en</ex></expan> mügen,
                                <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir das wol in geheim halten wollen.
                        Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
